boxd CLI license notice
=======================

No separate open-source license for the prebuilt boxd CLI binary was found in
the upstream installer, release manifests, website, or documentation at the
time this package was added.

The boxd CLI is distributed by Azin Tech Holding as part of the boxd services.
Use of the services is governed by the boxd Terms & Conditions:

  https://boxd.sh/terms/

The terms identify Azin Tech Holding as the operator of boxd.sh and state that
the Company owns the Services and related intellectual property. They grant
users a non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to access and use
the Services for internal business purposes.

This AUR package does not bundle the upstream binary in the git repository; it
declares upstream download URLs so makepkg retrieves the binary directly from
boxd.sh during package builds.
